Dennis Wyndham (15 Jenụwarị 1887 - 19 Ọgọst 1973) bụ onye na-eme ihe nkiri na ihe nkiri na South Africa. Ọ nọrọ ogologo oge na Britain, ọ pụtara na ihe karịrị ihe nkiri ịrị ano n'etiti 1920 na 1956
A mụrụ ya na Natal, South Africa.
Na 23 Mee 1917, ọ lụrụ Elsie Mackay nke a makwaara dị ka onye na-eme ihe nkiri na-adịghị ekwu okwu Poppy Wyndham
Ọpụpụ ya mere ka nna ya James Mackay, 1st Earl of Inchcape napụ ya ihe nketa
A kagburu alụmdi na nwunye ahụ na 1922.
